      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and bargain hunters! This vehicle is ready for a fresh start and presents a wonderful opportunity for someone looking for a hands-on project. While it currently requires some mechanical repairs and cosmetic updates to get back to its best, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get into a car with great potential. If you enjoy bringing cars back to life, this is the perfect project for you!",
