    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics thanks to refreshed bushings and a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension. While the exterior displays minor patina expected of a well-driven enthusiast vehicle, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A turn-key driver's car for those who prioritize mechanical precision and documented maintenance history.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
