    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-maintained premium sedan that perfectly balances sophisticated style with reliable performance. The exterior finish retains a brilliant luster, showing only minor, expected signs of careful road use, while the body panels remain straight and free of significant blemishes. Stepping inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seating surfaces are supple with only light natural creasing, and the high-gloss wood accents remain vibrant. All interior amenities, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seating, and the high-fidelity audio system, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, benefiting from a documented history of regular synthetic oil changes and a recent comprehensive inspection. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the vehicle handles with precision on a set of high-quality tires with significant tread life remaining. This car represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a turn-key luxury experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
